snippet.title: Appeal to find missing Victorian woman
snippet.content: Police have appealed for information into the whereabouts of a missing Victorian woman after her backpack was found on a Gold Coast beach. Gail Elizabeth Oliver's bag was found by a member of the public on Kurrawa Beach about 6.15am on Monday. A search of the beach and water failed to locate the 40-year-old, who has been reported missing in her home state. (C) AAP 2017
